00:36:40.693 --> 00:36:45.067
HAVE 1,000 ISSUES IN A ROW OF,
JUST IS UTTERLY UNIMAGINABLE TO

00:36:45.068 --> 00:36:50.225
THAT INNER KID IN ME.
