00:36:51.857 --> 00:36:53.312
EXCITING.
&gt;&gt; I'D ALSO ADD THAT WHEN I WAS

00:36:53.313 --> 00:36:57.172
A KID, AND I'D BE AT A GENERAL
NEWS STAND -- THIS IS BEFORE

00:36:58.834 --> 00:37:00.834
COMIC SHOPS, SO IT'S JUST

00:37:02.157 --> 00:37:04.157
GENERAL NEWSSTAND -- AND I COULD

