00:37:30.255 --> 00:37:34.359
LINE IMPACTED ME IN TERMS OF NOT
JUST BEING A KID WHO WENT TO 7

00:37:34.360 --> 00:37:38.081
ELEVEN AND GRABBED THE COPPIC TO
DRAW STUFF BUT ACTUALLY WANTED

00:37:38.082 --> 00:37:43.212
TO READ A CONTINUING STORY.
IF YOU WOULD HAVE ASKED ME,

00:37:44.432 --> 00:37:46.432
THERE'S ONE COMIC BOOK MOMENT
THAT WOULD PROBABLY NEVER BE

00:37:47.337 --> 00:37:49.618
ADAPTED TO LIVE ACTION FILM, I
WOULD SAY IT WAS KILLING

00:37:50.032 --> 00:37:52.918
SUPERMAN.
