00:37:52.919 --> 00:37:57.809
HAPPEN, AND WHETHER YOU LIKED IT
OR NOT BATMAN VERSUS SUPERMAN,

00:37:57.810 --> 00:38:02.154
DAWN OF JUSTICE.
NOW, I REMEMBER, BECAUSE I LIKE

00:38:02.155 --> 00:38:04.822
TO PRIDE MYSELF ON THINKING I
