THINK TO YOURSELF AND
SAY:  WOW, I WASN'T EXPECTING

00:38:21.171 --> 00:38:23.443
THAT TO EVER BE ADAPTED INTO A
MOVIE?

00:38:25.669 --> 00:38:28.172
&gt;&gt; I THINK IN THE BACK OF MY
HEAD, BECAUSE RIGHT AWAY, THERE

00:38:28.173 --> 00:38:31.645
WERE -- THERE WAS BOTH A
NOVELIZATION.

00:38:34.113 --> 00:38:36.113
THEY ALSO DID AUDIO BOOKS OF IT
THAT I THOUGHT WE WOULD

00:38:37.170 --> 00:38:39.205
EVENTUALLY GET THERE, ESPECIALLY
BECAUSE IT HAD COME UP EARLIER

00:38:39.206 --> 00:38:42.691
ANYWAY WITH THE TIM BURTON FILM.
THEN THEY DID IT AS AN ANIMATED

00:38:42.692 --> 00:38:44.692
MOVIE SO I THOUGHT YEAH, WE MATE

00:38:47.814 --> 00:38:49.265
JUST GET THERE AT SOME POINT SO
WHAT WAS -- IT WAS COOL TO SEE

00:38:49.266 --> 00:38:52.944
IT DONE BUT I THINK WHAT REALLY
HIT ME AS I WAS SITTING IN THE

