AND TO SEE THEM TRY AND

00:39:13.106 --> 00:39:15.166
REPRODUCE SOMETHING ON FILM THAT
I HAD DRAWN, ALMOST LIKE

00:39:17.850 --> 00:39:19.850
VERBATIM A LITTLE BIT, THAT WAS
A THRILL.

00:39:20.928 --> 00:39:22.928
&gt;&gt; THAT'S GOT TO BE COOL.
