FIRST -- CAN YOU REMEMBER YOUR
FIRST EXPERIENCE WITH THIS

00:39:47.257 --> 00:39:49.517
CHARACTER, WHEN YOU FIRST
DISCOVERED HIM?

00:39:51.758 --> 00:39:53.758
&gt;&gt; I THINK IT WAS WATCHING THE
GEORGE REEVES SHOWS ON THE

00:39:55.045 --> 00:39:57.045
LITTLE BLACK AND WHITE TV AT
HOME.

00:39:58.767 --> 00:40:01.451
THE COMIC COMES INTO MY LIFE,
