THE FIRST COMIC THAT WAS MINE
WAS ACTION 300, WHICH A

00:40:14.106 --> 00:40:16.106
BABYSITTER BROUGHT TO SHUT ME UP
ONE NIGHT WHEN I WAS ABOUT 5

