IT HAD SUPERMAN ON THE LEFT SIDE
OF THE COVER AND CRYPTOWAS

00:40:48.155 --> 00:40:50.155
BARKING AT HIM AND WEARING THE
CAPE.

00:40:50.791 --> 00:40:52.221
HE DOES NOT HAVE THE CAPE ON.
SUPERMAN IS SAYING OR THINKING,

00:40:52.222 --> 00:40:55.683
BECAUSE THEY DID THOUGHT
BALLOONS IN THOSE DAYS, SAID

00:40:57.940 --> 00:40:59.765
EVEN MY DOG CRYPTO DOESN'T
RECOGNIZE ME WHICH IF YOU'RE A

00:40:59.766 --> 00:41:02.443
KID, ALL RIGHT, I'LL BUY THAT.
