00:41:05.542 --> 00:41:07.542
SO MY FIRST COMIC WAS A SUPERMAN
COMIC.

00:41:08.198 --> 00:41:10.651
&gt;&gt; FOR THE RECORD MY FIRST WAS
WHEN HE REVEALED HIS IDENTITY TO

00:41:10.652 --> 00:41:12.883
LOIS.
WHICH WAS IN ACTION COMICS.

00:41:13.893 --> 00:41:15.314
&gt;&gt; THAT WAS A POINT OF SOME
DISCUSSION, BECAUSE WHEN THAT

00:41:15.315 --> 00:41:18.377
STORY WAS ORIGINALLY PLANNED,
AND WE HAD A GROUP OF WRITERS IN

00:41:18.378 --> 00:41:21.864
THE ROOM THAT TALKED ABOUT IT
