THE GRAND SCHEME OF THINGS
NOBODY CARED.

00:57:49.457 --> 00:57:51.113
THE RUN THAT DAN WORKED ON WITH
MIKE CARLIN AND THE WHOLE REST

00:57:51.114 --> 00:57:56.084
OF THE TEAM, WHETHER IT WAS
BECAUSE IT FIRST HIT -- THE NEWS

00:57:56.085 --> 00:58:00.195
OF IT FIRST HIT ON A SLOW NEWS
DAY OR THE ZEITGEIST OF THE

00:58:02.077 --> 00:58:04.982
WORLD HAD CHANGED, A BUNCH OF
THINGS CAME TOGETHER, AND WE

00:58:06.645 --> 00:58:09.357
WERE JUST STANDING THERE WITH A
BASKET CATCHING MANNA FROM

00:58:11.827 --> 00:58:14.336
HEAVEN FOR A WHILE.
THIS WAS A VERY EARLY DAYS OF

00:58:14.337 --> 00:58:18.255
DOING ANY KIND OF GRAPHIC NOVEL
FORMAT TRADE PAPERBACK OR

00:58:23.016 --> 00:58:25.871
ANYTHING, AND WE WANTED TO DO A
ONE-VOLUME EDITION OF THE FIRST

00:58:25.872 --> 00:58:29.794
DEATH STORY.
