&gt;&gt; SOUNDS ABOUT RIGHT.
&gt;&gt; THAT'S WHAT WAS REALLY A

00:59:39.399 --> 00:59:41.275
MIRACLE IS THE SPEED WITH WHICH
YOU PULLED IT TOGETHER.

00:59:41.276 --> 00:59:43.331
&gt;&gt; NORMALLY SPEAKING, YOU'D
EXPECT IF YOU WERE SUCCESSFUL

00:59:43.332 --> 00:59:46.832
FOR SOMETHING LIKE THAT TO SELL
HALF OF THE COPIES YOU SHIPPED,

00:59:46.833 --> 00:59:50.523
MAYBE 1/3 OF THE COPIES AND THE
REST WOULD COME BACK AND BE DEAD

00:59:50.524 --> 00:59:54.240
TREES.
