GAMBLE THIS THIS YEAR AND WE

01:00:13.962 --> 01:00:15.962
PRINTED THE 650,000, OR WHATEVER
IT WAS, AND WE SENT IT OUT.

01:00:18.435 --> 01:00:20.683
AND THEY ALL SOLD.
IT WAS AN AMAZING YEAR.

